We believe that home cooking should always be fun, interesting, and easy to do! Enjoy our collection of fun and easy food tutorials! With recipes ranging from healthy dinners to sugary sweet delights, there are a plethora of creative options to spice up your home cooking. Follow us:Facebook: http://bit.ly/SoYummyFBInstagram: http://bit.ly/SoYummyIGWebsite: https://soyummy.com/#SoYummy  #Dumpling #StayHomeDumpling DoughPrep Time1 hourDifficultyEasy Total Time1 hour Yield30-35 dumpling wrappersIngredients2 ¬º cups flour¬æ cup warm water (between 110-120¬∞F)Pinch of salt (optional)Instructions1. In a medium bowl, combine the flour and warm water until it becomes shaggy. With your hands, knead the shaggy dough inside the bowl until it comes together to form a ball. Cover the bowl with a damp towel and let rest for 15 minutes.2. After resting, transfer the ball of dough onto a clean surface and knead firmly until it becomes smooth and elastic (about 2-4 minutes.) Cover with a damp cloth and rest again, for 30 minutes.3. After the second rest, take your thumb and press firmly into the center of the dough ball. Using both hands, begin to squeeze and stretch the dough until you create a big donut shape with a large hole in the center. 4. Slice the ‚Äúdonut‚Äù into even pieces of desired size. Keep covered with a damp cloth, and when ready to use, roll pieces out individually into thin wrappers. (Optional: Trim wrappers using a large circle cookie cutter, for a clean edge.)5. title: Dikabarkan Gantikan Kim Jong Un, Kim Yo Jong, Dinilai Bisa Lebih Kejam
tags: Tribunnews|tribun video|tribun|Dikabarkan|Gantikan|Kim Jong Un|Kim Yo Jong|Dinilai|Bisa|Lebih Kejam
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Adik pemimpin Korea Utara, Kim Jong Un, Kim Yo Jong dikabarkan akan memegang tampuk kekuasaan. Kim Yo Jong dinilai bisa lebih kejam dari sang kakak. Kim Jong Un sejak berkuasa pada 2011 menjadi perbincangan dunia lantaran tidak hanya bertindak tanpa ampun pada lawan politik, namun juga keluarganya. Pakar menyatakan Kim Yo Jong tidak kalah keras dan kejam dari sang kakak. Dikutip oleh Kompas.com dari Daily Mirror, Minggu (26/4/2020), Profesor Natasha Lindstaedt mengatakan, gender bukan jadi penghalang sang adik untuk menjadi tiran baru. Saya tidak percaya posisinya sebagai perempuan bakal melemahkan posisinya jika dia memegang kekuasaan, beber Profesor Lindstaedt.Dia menerangkan, keluarga Kim tidak dilihat sebagai manusia biasa oleh rakyat Korea Utara, mereka dianggap sebagai wakil Tuhan yang akan mengurusi segalanya.Lindstaedt menjelaskan, jika Kim Yo Jong berkuasa, maka dia juga akan dianggap sebagai Tuhan sama seperti kakaknya tersebut. Sangat dimungkinkan dia akan mengambil pendekatan yang lebih kejam dari kakaknya terhadap dunia karena level kemiskinan yang mereka alami, paparnya. Lindstaedt mengatakan, dia yakin Kim adik bakal lebih tegas dari kakaknya. Apalagi, dia sering terlihat di muka umum akhir-akhir ini. Profesor Lindstaedt melanjutkan, sangat mungkin Kim adik merasa bahwa dia perlu lebih tegas dari kakaknya jika dia berkuasa.Oleh Kim, dia dipercaya sebagai utusan negara komunis itu, dan mendampingi kakaknya saat bertemu Presiden Korsel Moon Jae-in dan Presiden AS Donald Trump.Ia digadang-gadang menjadi kandidat terkuat memimpin negeri komunis itu, karena putra Kim Jong Un dianggap masih terlalu muda. Sementara kakak tertua mereka, Kim Jong Chul, dianggap sebagai playboy yang tak tertarik dengan politik sehingga tidak dianggap sebagai ahli waris.(Tribun-Video.com/Kompas.com)Artikel ini telah tayang di Kompas.com dengan judul Adik Kim Jong Un, Kim Yo Jong, Dinilai Bisa Lebih Kejam dari Sang Kakak, https://www.kompas.com/global/read/2020/04/25/195708170/adik-kim-jong-un-kim-yo-jong-dinilai-bisa-lebih-kejam-dari-sang-kakak?page=all#page2.Penulis : Ardi Priyatno UtomoEditor : Ardi Priyatno Utomo

title: Watch the Pentagon's three declassified UFO videos taken by U.S. Navy pilots
tags: Bottom Line|CNBC|business news|finance stock|stock market|news channel|news station|breaking news|us news|world news|cable|cable news|finance news|money|money tips
description: The declassification of the videos late Monday was to clear up any misconceptions by the public on whether or not the footage that has been circulating was real, the Pentagon said in a statement Monday. The footage, which shows unidentified objects flying at high speeds in the Earth's atmosphere along with audio of Navy pilots expressing shock and awe, was initially leaked in 2007 and 2017. The U.S. Navy formalized a reporting process last year for pilots to report incidents of UFO sightings.The Department of Defense released three videos taken by U.S. Navy pilots revealing mysterious flying objects that to this day remain unidentified. The declassification of the videos late Monday, one of which was taken in 2004 and the subsequent two taken in 2015, was meant to ‚Äúclear up any misconceptions by the public on whether or not the footage that has been circulating was real, or whether or not there is more to the videos,‚Äù the Pentagon said in a statement Monday. The footage, which shows unidentified objects flying at high speeds in the Earth‚Äôs atmosphere along with audio of Navy pilots expressing shock and awe, was initially leaked in 2007 and 2017. The videos were taken during training flights and the 2017 leaks were published by the New York Times.  ‚ÄúThe U.S. Navy previously acknowledged that these videos circulating in the public domain were indeed Navy videos,‚Äù the Pentagon‚Äôs statement read. ‚ÄúAfter a thorough review, the department has determined that the authorized release of these unclassified videos does not reveal any sensitive capabilities or systems, and does not impinge on any subsequent investigations of military air space incursions by unidentified aerial phenomena.‚Äù‚ÄúThe aerial phenomena observed in the videos remain characterized as ‚Äòunidentified‚Äô,‚Äù it said. title: Ngaji Jomblo 01: Biar Nggak Nyesel Setelah Nikah
tags: felix|siauw|dakwah|anak muda
description: Manusia memang selalu dijanjikam harapan di depannya, dan dibebani dengan penyesalan di belakangnya. Begitu pun juga bagi mereka yang ingin menikah, tentu mereka berharap pasangan yang terbaik, walau akhirnya menyesal ketika setelah menikah lalu menemui yang lebih baikMencari pasangan, seperti mencari kayu bakar di hutan, dimana kita hanya boleh mengambil satu kayu bakar, dan tak boleh berjalan mundur. Lalu seperti apa cara mendapatkan pasangan terbaik untuk hidup kita?Bagaimana cara agar kita tak menyesali apa yang sudah kita pilih, sekaligus disaat yang sama tidak menjadikan diri kita panjang angan-angan?
